  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface TransitionFactory<S extends State,T extends Transition>
extends org.jgrapht.EdgeFactory<State,Transition>
    contains the factory that is used to create the transition of a Buchi automaton or of an incomplete Buchi automaton
